title: Legion MKVI Tactical Squad
description:
Troops in advanced MKVI 'Corvus Armour'
Build the core of a Legiones Astartes army with two 10-man units or one 20-man unit
Upgrade your squads with command gear, bayonets, and customisable Sergeants

title: Legion Cataphractii Terminator Squad
description:
Elites clad in robust Cataphractii armour
Builds 10 Terminators, armed as dedicated melee fighters or versatile combatants
Bolster your Legiones Astartes with the heaviest form of Terminator armour

title: Legion MKVI Assault Squad
description:
Highly mobile close combat troops for Legiones Astartes armies
Builds 10 Assault Legionaries, armed with chainswords and bolt pistols
Upgrade your squad with combat shields and Sergeant wargear

title: MKVI Legion Command Squad
description:
Surround your Legiones Astartes leaders with a mighty Command Squad for Warhammer: The Horus Heresy
Chosen warriors with lethal wargear, clad in decorated MKVI 'Corvus' power armour
Proudly bear your Legion standards onto the battlefield

title: MKIII Tactical Squad
description:
Warriors in classic MKIII 'Iron Armour'
Build the core of a Legiones Astartes army with a solid unit of 20 models or two units of 10 models
Upgrade your squads with command gear, bayonets, and customisable Sergeants

title: Legion MKIV Destroyer Squad
description:
Specialised infantry armed with destructive, forbidden weapons to scour the land
Equipped with Tigrus pattern bolt pistols, a rad-missile launcher, and three optional Phosphex bombs
An Elites choice for most Legions
This resin modelling kit is a collectible item and construction should only be undertaken by expert Warhammer hobbyists aged 15 years and over

title: Legion Cataphractii Praetor & Chaplain Consul
description:
A pair of powerful HQ choices to command your Legiones Astartes armies
The Chaplain Consul is armed with fierce charisma and a deadly Crozius Arcanum
The Praetorâ€™s Cataphractii armour shrugs off all but the most grievous wounds

title: Spartan Assault Tank
description:
An indomitable Heavy Support transport for all Legiones Astartes armies
Carry whole squads of Legionaries and Terminators while laying down fire support
Terrifyingly durable, unexpectedly fast, and utterly deadly

title: Contemptor Dreadnought
description:
A versatile Elites choice for all Legiones Astartes armies
A huge arsenal of punishing weapons, with a chassis that can take a beating
Customise your Dreadnought with a variety of accessories and poses

title: Leviathan Siege Dreadnought with Ranged Weapons
description:
A gargantuan Heavy Support choice for all Legiones Astartes armies
A nigh-invincible behemoth, armed with an array of massively powerful weapons
Customise your Dreadnought with a variety of armour plates and poses
